          <source>The following example uses the                      <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.MatrixAnimationUsingPath&gt;</ph> object to animate the                      <ph id="ph2">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.MatrixTransform.Matrix%2A&gt;</ph> property of a                      <ph id="ph3">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.MatrixTransform&gt;</ph>.</source>
